{"tid":838381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【機票加價】11月起准徵燃油附加費 國泰長途來回加$1,304","createTime":"2018-09-27T05:23:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T07:27:01.000Z","uid":212249,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2fbbdc4f354c801dd6266445fd79e564e0f74515","tid":838381,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T05:23:31.000Z","msg":"早前民航處新規定：11月1日起航空公司可向香港出發的航班徵收燃油附加費，一改2016年初訂立的免收規例。國泰航空昨日公佈即將收取的燃油附加費，長途航線如香港飛往美國、歐洲、澳紐等收費為單程652港元，短途航線則收單程146港元，變相長途來回的機票加價1,304港元。里數達人小斯提醒：「以後用里數換最低門檻的台北機票，都要多付來回292港元，所以最好11月前兌換機票。之前已換的機票，一旦要重新出票，亦要加付燃油附加費。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/all/realtime/article/20180927/58729103\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fall%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180927%2F58729103&d=tN%2B0qkwPELLOhdsQkewfwv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=e59eaa44\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fall%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180927%2F58729103&h=ecef71de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/all/realtime/article/20180927/58729103</a>"},{"pid":"b6ac673a4cb1b170bef657a0b03027285534ba11","tid":838381,"uid":4531,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T05:28:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c3608e4b36e8ccc16b48c77998ebdebe3c1498f0","tid":838381,"uid":2679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T05:29:32.000Z","msg":"貴好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ea8f3778a7c56aa7d7da40ad8257402aa9cb25f","tid":838381,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T05:30:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5be29279ef8329c86ad19a58e62f0665223108ce","tid":838381,"uid":121146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T05:31:30.000Z","msg":"多謝港共"},{"pid":"bf949506c44e03ec5d395ef6e500dbe1